41.000Z","msg":"主席 fat fat啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd94ec4c50690a89a4b1b87e3c1a5648d69a518","tid":1144994,"uid":185022,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"a13a13a7a3421ee32eb4e893305a17c367232c3c","tid":1144994,"uid":20241,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:52:23.000Z","msg":"終於有足夠醫生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生我個頭赤赤痛呀<br />\n請說普通話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"港:醫生,我個胃拿住拿住<br />\n蝗:不會普通話的沒有人權,看甚麼醫生?下一個。<br />\n<br />\n港:醫生,你枝針打左兩個人啦喎~<br />\n蝗:甚麼兩個人?是兩個禮拜啦～<br />\n<br />\n港:我幾時有得做手術?<br />\n蝗:看你給多少錢。<br />\n<br />\n港:醫生,我表弟冇心跳呀,快啲急救啦<br />\n蝗:我不會心肺復甦法<br />\n<br />\n港:點解我生完仔會冇左個腎。<br />\n蝗:就拿一個而已,有甚麼問題。<br />\n<br />\n港:醫生,你做咩割割下包皮叫醒我?<br />\n蝗:價錢加到100萬,不然我現在就離開。<br />\n<br />\n諗到三年後係祖国高質醫生幫助下香港醫療可以大大改善就扯扯地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6590f8e5e5466c9ed67b16fe1fddceea51868251","tid":1144994,"uid":177590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"要移民真係唔洗猶疑<br />\n走到既好即時走"},{"pid":"7f22dfd725e512185670eb5ba1d7764dedd5a3f9","tid":1144994,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a13a13a7a3421ee32eb4e893305a17c367232c3c","tid":1144994,"uid":20241,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:52:23.000Z","msg":"終於有足夠醫生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生我個頭赤赤痛呀<br />\n請說普通話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"和歌頭 check check 通"},{"pid":"bf583d98b082b51b7ba0b7bdadfd73ada3cf6998","tid":1144994,"uid":236171,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"760b6951ba60ffe50d146b890c9de225ff7c9e77","tid":1144994,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:05:54.000Z","msg":"方案七重點<br />\n<br />\n在醫管局、衞生署或2間醫學院工作滿3年，通過<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>執業試</strong></span></span>後，可免實習。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"問題係，醫療機構三年工作沒規定一定要做臨床工作，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可做行政工作</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n第一， 即使考完執業試（包括臨床試），都唔能夠完全了解外來醫生日常臨床經驗同醫德等等嘅實際實踐情況。<br />\n<br />\n好簡單，你要問針筒可唔可以重用，小學生都識答唔可以。但係做落係咪個個都跟足規矩？同埋宜家咁講，同請個Manager 六個月 probation 可以包括洗廁所經驗有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n第二，容許非臨床經驗納入工作期限，醫生根本唔需要同前線醫護人員丶同袍或病人有任何溝通同交流。喺語言同文化差異處理上都無保證。你肯定咁對醫療服務質素唔會帶黎負面影響？"},{"pid":"27410820a29386615e734d0346c8e3252cc484b1","tid":1144994,"uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:42:46.000Z","msg":"投票唔啱投到啱<br />\n cls"},{"pid":"8016793c5d4e0feca973dade11c94b8ab8af976c","tid":1144994,"uid":34730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"你說什麼？我聽不懂"},{"pid":"ff2ceb0a6bca0710e417c6d90f5c471497f8b6e6","tid":1144994,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"就算料夠但冇醫德<br />\n有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e072308e7fa4b4789667ca97bb4785a8de5ab55","tid":1144994,"uid":157362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"923d77c2ec19c5f3ec349aa7e5527fab129da264","tid":1144994,"uid":105822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bf583d98b082b51b7ba0b7bdadfd73ada3cf6998","tid":1144994,"uid":236171,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"760b6951ba60ffe50d146b890c9de225ff7c9e77","tid":1144994,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:05:54.000Z","msg":"方案七重點<br />\n<br />\n在醫管局、衞生署或2間醫學院工作滿3年，通過<span style=\"color: orange;\"><